The paper discusses the improvement of the development process of a software start-up by introducing agile practices, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of code metrics, which is related to software development (cs.SD) and computer engineering (cs.CE). The paper also discusses the impact of the introduced agile practices on the employees, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper mentions the selection and implementation of agile practices, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL).
